v1.01 :
- Reorganized code for better options management (parsing is partially automated).
- Command-line options now respect POSIX conventions.
- Added version print (using -V or --version).
- All french messages have been translated.

v1.0 :
- Created UsbMount for WSL environments.
- Simple "--help" command, executed when no options are supplied.
- "-u" option to unmount.
- Very simple (and dirty) command argument parser, that should be automated in the future.
